---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Podcasts | Paige Niedringhaus" description="Talking about code is almost as fun as writing it. I've co-hosted three podcasts over the past few years — here's where to find them.">
  <div class="page-container">
    <h1>Podcasts</h1>

    <section>
      <p>
        Talking about code is almost as fun as writing it. I've co-hosted three podcasts over the past few years — here's where to find them.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Front-end Fire</h2>
      <div class="podcast-feature">
        <img src="/thumbnails/front-end-fire.png" alt="Front-end Fire logo" class="podcast-logo" />
        <div class="podcast-description">
          <p>
            <a href="https://twitter.com/jherr" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Jack Herrington</a>,
            <a href="https://twitter.com/tjvantoll" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">TJ VanToll</a>,
            and I started <a href="https://front-end-fire.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Front-end Fire</a>
            in 2023 to keep developers up to speed on what's happening in the frontend world — new frameworks, browser updates, the drama, all of it. New episodes every Monday.
          </p>
          <a href="https://front-end-fire.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="podcast-cta">
            Listen to Front-end Fire &rarr;
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>PodRocket</h2>
      <div class="podcast-feature">
        <img src="/thumbnails/podRocket.png" alt="PodRocket logo" class="podcast-logo" />
        <div class="podcast-description">
          <p>
            I joined LogRocket's <a href="https://podrocket.logrocket.com/hosts/paige-niedringhaus" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">PodRocket</a>
            as a co-host in 2023. Each episode I sit down with someone doing interesting work in web development and we get into it.
          </p>
          <a href="https://podrocket.logrocket.com/hosts/paige-niedringhaus" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="podcast-cta">
            See all PodRocket episodes &rarr;
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>React Round Up</h2>
      <div class="podcast-feature">
        <img src="/thumbnails/reactRoundUp.png" alt="React Round Up logo" class="podcast-logo" />
        <div class="podcast-description">
          <p>
            From 2020 to 2023 I co-hosted <a href="https://topenddevs.com/podcasts/react-round-up/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">React Round Up</a>
            — deep dives into the React ecosystem with guests from across the community. The archive is still worth a listen.
          </p>
          <a href="https://topenddevs.com/podcasts/react-round-up/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="podcast-cta">
            Browse React Round Up episodes &rarr;
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .podcast-feature {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: var(--space-6);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .podcast-logo {
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    object-fit: contain;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  }

  .podcast-description {
    flex: 1;

    & p {
      font-size: var(--text-lg);
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
      color: var(--color-text);
    }
  }

  .podcast-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;

    &:hover {
      color: var(--color-accent);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .podcast-feature {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .podcast-logo {
      width: 100px;
      height: 100px;
    }
  }
</style>
